includedAssets.title: Finding Nemo
includedAssets.synopsis: A clownfish scours the ocean for his son, who has been caught and put in a dentist's aquarium. Pixar adventure with the voice of Ellen DeGeneres.

includedAssets.title: Finding Dory
includedAssets.synopsis: Thirteen years after Nemo was found, friendly-but-forgetful blue tang fish Dory (voiced by Ellen DeGeneres) sets off on a submarine adventure to find her parents years after she lost touch. Aided by her best buddy clownfish Marlin (Albert Brooks) and his son Nemo (Hayden Rolence) it's a quest fraught with danger including a predatory giant squid. However, some old friends turn up to help (whale shark Destiny and beluga whale Bailey) and she also swims into resourceful red octopus Hank (Ed O'Neill). Superlative sequel from the Pixar team.
includedAssets.shortSynopsis: Nemo and dad Marlin set out on a crazy underwater adventure to help their forgetful friend Dory to find her mum and dad. Animated sequel.
